title: Petunia the Piggy Bank
description: The kids start getting an allowance but only Petunia thinks to save for something special.

title: Cabeza de Dragon
description: Manzana y Cebollín deben hacer funcionar un estacionamiento secreto en su terraza para poder darse una ducha.

title: #WorkingStiff
description: After Babs hooks Karen up with a job at the Burrito Bucket the two heroes encounter a new villain, the scourge of the fast-food underworld, the Condiment King!

title: Ain't That a Kick in the Side?
description: After Witch Way teases Prohyas by calling him, "Vambre's sidekick," Prohyas intensifies his efforts to prove them wrong.

title: Captain Bamboozle
description: Mr. Mxyzptlk decides to create some mischief by endowing Shazam's well-meaning Uncle Dudley with superpowers bigger than anyone in the league.

title: And Then There Was Ben
description: Professor Paradox unites the good Bens from across all dimensions to take on Vilgax, Eon, and the evil Bens in the ultimate showdown!

title: Hyde & Zeke
description: Craig and his friends are challenged to find the greatest hider that Hide and Seek has ever known.

title: Drawn to Sports with Hannah
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Hannah competes in track and field.

title: Cat Man Do/Impeach Fuzz
description: Cat Man Do: Bubbles saves a seemingly innocent kitty from the clutches of an evil villain. But when the girls discover it's actually the Cat who is evil, they must save the Professor from being the next victim./Impeach Fuzz: When Fuzzy Lumkins throws his hat into the mayoral ring and claims a surprise victory, it's up to the Mayor and the girls to wrestle the office, and the Mayor's actual hat, back from him.

title: Rise and Funshine
description: Funshine learns he can be as fearless as one of his super hero comic book characters when the Team falls into a magical sleep. To awaken them, he must transport them in the Cloudseeker to a special place in the Silver Lining - but he has never driven it before, and must learn from a comical "How To Pilot the Cloudseeker" video hosted by Grumpy.

title: That Ol' Time Rock Rolls!/Make Like a Banana and Split
description: When Big Old Boulder rolls down the hill towards the museum, Berta needs the Mechas help to keep it stable./It's Food Day in Pretty Big City, but the Mechas need to help when the banana atop the banana split statue is not split!

title: Last One Out of Beach City
description: Pearl, Steven and Amethyst go to a rock show.

title: Accion Roja al Futuro
description: Cuando convocan a Acción Roja a una batalla épica en el futuro, Enid no está segura de lo que debe hacer.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: De vuelta a la accion roja
description: Enid se alía a Acción Roja para enfrentarse a una amenaza del futuro.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: Fashion Bears
description: In order to abide by the clothing policy of their favorite Boba shop, the Bears get some new outfits. But with new looks come new lives including office work, fashion modeling and even falling in love!

title: Appreciation Day
description: By trying to change Benson's opinion of them, Mordecai and Rigby accidentally create lots of work for themselves.

title: Game Show
description: While shopping with his Mom, Clarence discovers Breehn hiding in a clothes rack. Under the guise of trying on new clothes for their moms, they sneak out to find a local gameshow being hosted inside the Aberdale Mall.

title: The Beepers: The Visitor
description: The Beepers find the perfect groove after a new friend shreds a little too hard.

title: The Curse
description: Craig, Kelsey and JP run afoul of some no-good teenage witches and are cursed! Lousy teenagers!

title: Sunken Treasure
description: A relaxing beach day becomes an underwater adventure when Unikitty and her friends find a message in a bottle.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Dumbrella
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, have been traveling on the back of a truck in the rain for days. Charlie produces an umbrella to help his friend but unfortunately it's a "dumbrella" and it's looking to have some fun with them!

title: The Vampire Strikes Back
description: Ben, Rook, and Rad Dudesman come face to face with the evil Lord Transyl, a vampire-like alien who can make anyone his loyal slave! (Introducing new Ben alien, Whampire.)

title: TP2: Judgement Bidet
description: When the city experiences a toilet paper shortage Beth and Harold investigate and discover it's their old rival Sewer Mike who is the mastermind behind it all.

title: Let's Meet Sonic
description: When world class hero SONIC THE HEDGEHOG visits the plaza, he teams up with KO to save the day.

title: Top of the Titans: Best Love Songs
description: The Titans follow their heart with songs devoted to their greatest relationships: Beast Boy & Raven, Cyborg & Jinx and the Titans & Food.

title: The Unikingdom Awards
description: Unikitty throws an elaborate award show for everyone in the Unikingdom, including Master Frown and Brock, but tensions rise when Frown fails to win an award.

title: Gryffindor v Hufflepuff
description: Dame Helen Mirren hosts the first episode of this epic TV event series. Over 4 episodes the Houses of Hogwarts will do battle to see which team knows the most about the wizarding world, featuring celebrity guests, actors from the original films and more Harry Potter Magic than you could find on a day trip to Diagon Alley. Tonight's match up sees the brave Gryffindors face the loyal Hufflepuffs for a guaranteed place in the grand finale.
originalseriesname: Harry Potter: Hogwarts Tournament of Houses

title: Fixing a Flonk
description: Wanting to stop Flonk from being an evildoer for good, Prohyas tries to find Flonk a permanent venue for his nasty comedy. Vambre, however, wants to deliver him to the cops as usual.

title: Cambia de Parecer
description: Steven se enfrenta al mayor desafío de su vida.

title: Clayton
description: Darwin needs to find a photo of Clayton to put on the cover of the school yearbook - but he makes the mistake of seeking help from Tobias, who has his eye on the cover spot himself! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Mind Your Manners
description: The babies learn proper dinner etiquette when preparing to dine out with Granny.

title: #Powerless
description: Supergirl loses her powers and, with the help of BumbleBee, must rely on her street smarts to save Garth from vengeful Toyman.

title: Top of the Titans:  Raddest Songs
description: From "Booty Scooty" to "Sour Grapes" to "The Night Begins to Shine," Birdarang is here to count down the raddest music from Teen Titans Go!

title: The Prank
description: Gumball and Darwin's harmless pranks on Dad spiral hopelessly out of control.

title: Drawn to Change
description: Cartoon Network is Drawn to Change, and Craig of the Creek talks to Martin Luther King Junior's granddaughter Yolanda about how kids can change the world!

title: The Power
description: Mordecai & Rigby find a mysterious keyboard that allows them to do anything they want, including accidently sending Benson to the moon.

title: El gran espectaculo
description: Steven filma un documental que sigue los pasos de una banda local mientras consiguen su primer gran oportunidad.

title: Whistle Woes
description: When Thomas's whistle suddenly stops working, he learns that he doesn't need his whistle to still be himself.
originalseriesname: Thomas and Friends: All Engines Go

title: Sheep Bears
description: The Bears get jobs as sheep herders on an idyllic farm.

title: Everything's Fine
description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

title: Skater Sumo
description: As Sumo and Clarence are playing outside, Chelsea and Rita skate by on their new skateboards. Enthralled, Sumo decides to build his own and join their skating team, while Clarence seems to have other ideas.

title: Red Action to the Future
description: When Red Action is called to the future for an epic battle, Enid is unsure of what to do.

title: The Anniversary Box
description: Craig is entrusted with a special anniversary gift for his mom, and immediately loses it in the Creek.

title: Zombozo-Land
description: Ben, Gwen and Max revisit their favorite amusement park, renovated and re-branded as AdrenaWORLD! Unfortunately, the new management is Zombozo and his trio of new henchmen! He's got a plan to hypnotize everyone in the park to form a criminal army. Ben has to set aside his desire to ride every ride in the park and make things right.

title: Ninjago Confidential
description: Back in Ninjago City, Zane and Pixal hit the mean streets to track down Milton Dyer, only to discover that things are not what they seem.

title: Not in My Backyard
description: Pocoyo discovers some old rubbish and decides to have a clear out. Baby Bird, Pato and Elly do the same. Soon there's a huge pile of rubbish, and it turns out it's on Caterpillar's doorstep. The rubbish keeps getting thrown around until finally Pocoyo follows the rubbish and realizes it's just going in a circle. In order to break the cycle, Pocoyo helps his friends make some new fun toys and games out of the rubbish.

title: Top of the Titans: Beast Boy & Cyborg Songs
description: Birdarang counts down the best musical moments from the raddest bros you know, Beast Boy and Cyborg. Waffles!

title: Vamoosh on the Loosh
description: Pocoyo promises to teach Baby Bird to drive the Vamoosh but keeps putting it off. Fed up, Baby Bird decides to have a go on his own but he doesn't know how. The Vamoosh spins out of control. Pocoyo realises he must keep to his promise and teach Baby Bird to drive properly.

title: Changeable Terraingable
description: Personality conflicts between Vambre and Prohyas come to a head as the Warriors miraculously manage to ace a mission at an ever changing labyrinth.

title: Petri
description: Apple and Onion must get back to their apartment to put the lid on their petri dish.

title: Ninjago Confidencial
description: De vuelta en la ciudad de Ninjago, Zane y Pixal salen a las calles para encontrar a Milton Dyer, y descubren que las cosas no son lo que parecen…

title: Weapon of Choice
description: Worried that his sword is a glorified consolation prize, Mao Mao sets out to prove the worth of his weapon.

title: Vambre's Guilty Pleasure
description: Vambre tries her best to keep her tough Warrior reputation intact and still go to the cutesy wootsy Piggiepie Jones stage show.

title: Bobo Chan
description: Badgerclops adopts an abandoned monster, but some things are better left in the wild.

title: Lego DC Super Hero Girls: Brain Drain
description: Missing memories provide an intriguing mystery for everyone's favorite young female heroes in this all-new animated film.  When Supergirl, Wonder Woman, Batgirl, Harley Quinn, Bumblebee, Poison Ivy and Katana suddenly realize they cannot remember a single moment from their Monday at Super Hero High, the young Super Heroes spring into sleuthing action! Suspecting foul-play, they band together to retrace their steps and uncover the mystery of who exactly stole their memories - and, what nefarious plan might be afoot?

title: Skateboard
description: Bing and Flop are in the park when Pando vooshes past on his skatebaord. Pando agrees to let Bing try out his skateboard. But what happens when Bing comes to a steep hill and the skateboard goes faster and faster?

title: Deb O'Nair
description: A classy queen of etiquette makes the Utoniums question their superhero way of life.

title: Drawn to Sports with Luke
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Luke is passionate about running, jumping and climbing in Ninja Racing.

title: #TheMinus
description: Diana receives her first ever A minus and becomes convinced that she needs to work harder, however, in order to do so, she resorts to rather drastic measures.

title: WaterHose-Five
description: The hottest day of the year and a broke air conditioner leads to a water battle of epic proportions to determine who controls the garden hose.

title: Monkey See, Doggie Do/Mommy Fearest
description: Monkey See, Doggie Do: Mojo unleashes a curse on Townsville that turns everyone into dogs, including the Powerpuff Girls! Luckily, they manage to sniff out a solution and show Mojo that their bite is worse than his bark./Mommy Fearest: When Professor Utonium falls for the lovely Ima Goodlady, the girls quickly discover that Ima's not such a good lady after all. She's really the sinister Sedusa!

title: Rotten Apple
description: Onion's Dad becomes convinced that Apple is a bad influence on his son.

title: Watermelon Gag
description: When Uncle Grandpa gets a watermelon stuck in his mouth, he is unable to ask for help and people interpret it as a comedy routine. As Uncle Grandpa's popularity rises, his friendships and morale suffer.

title: Pequeno
description: El legendario, gigantesco y crítico padre de Mao Mao visita a su hijo en su nuevo trabajo como sheriff.

title: Sarah
description: Darwin asks Sarah for a photo to put on the cover of the school yearbook. But when Sarah tries to help, things get a little sticky. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Justice League's Next Top Talent Idol Star: Dance Crew Edition Part 2
description: Robin is left without a dance crew so Vibe gives him lessons on how to be a world class break-dancer and team player.

title: Top of the Titans: Dance Party!
description: Come correct because it's a Titans Dance Battle! Birdarang reviews the greatest dance songs in Teen Titans Go! history.

title: The Inbetween
description: Apple and Onion have promised they will be there for Falafel's birthday party. However, they find themselves in a mysterious place and don't know how to get out.

title: Magnet Mayhem/Stop That Train
description: The magnet crane at the construction site accidentally turns on, sucking up all the metal, including the Mecha Builders!/Roof is delivering eggs to Marwyn at the Train Station, that is, until the train pulls into the station and can't stop!

title: A Pastime for Petunia
description: Petunia has a difficult time finding a hobby that doesn't imitate the other babies' interests.

title: Awesome Brawlers Training  Camp
description: The Awesome Brawlers head to a training facility owned by Kasami International to prepare for the Bakugan Battle League - Los Volmos. But once the gang figures out they will all be competing against each other for the same title, the "team building" retreat doesn't quite go as planned./Agit turns up at the Kasami training facility and fits right in with the Awesome brawlers. This is a lifestyle that he can get used to, but it becomes apparent Agit is torn between a life as a phantom thief and life as a brawler.

title: Wide Load Vacay: Big City Dancers
description: Two houses, Frank and Charlie, traveling on the back of a truck visit NYC where the rhythms of the city make Charlie wanna dance his little back porch off. Frank … not so much. But when you go far enough into the city, anything can happen.

title: Teachers
description: When Darwin asks his friends which teacher deserves to be on the yearbook cover, they struggle to find a single worthy candidate! Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Ketchup
description: BMO and Marceline swap stories about their recent adventures.

title: Collect This
description: Ben finally meets the ones responsible for his intergalactic TV show, and the actor who makes Ben 10 more famous than Ben himself!

title: Memory Mayhem
description: Frankie tries to discover more about the mysterious rock that bought them to their new home, with the help of an entity called The Head.

title: Drawn To Expression!
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating queer youth and families in the LGBTQIA+ community that radiate joy, pride, and inclusivity. We are championing the ways these kids and families form connections to their authentic selves by expressing their creativity and queer identity through their art.

title: Olvideti
description: Ben, Gwen y Max van de excursión en busca de un Forgeti legendario, un yeti que hace que las personas se olviden de que lo vieron, pero cuando el Doctor Ánimo reúne a los Forgeti para su plan de robar bancos sin que nadie los recuerde, Ben aprende muy pronto que el Forgeti es más que un simple mito.

title: Ranger Tabes
description: To recover a missing package, the Bears get help from Ranger Tabes, an eccentric forest ranger. But her overblown sense of justice might be too much for the Bears to handle.

title: Bear Cleanse
description: A doctor tells the Bears to go on a cleanse to improve their health. But when Grizz realizes he can only eat what grizzly bears eat, he starts to lose his mind.

title: Stakes Part 7: Checkmate
description: On the eve of battle, Marceline's archenemy comes to her with a strange proposal.

title: We Baby Bears: BHA Bha Song
description: We Baby Bears follows baby bear brothers Grizz, Panda, and Ice Bear as they journey in a magical box to fantastic different worlds in search of their perfect home.

title: Pulling Your Weight
description: Apple and Onion join a gym to gain the strength of seven people.

title: Small
description: Mao Mao's legendary, gigantic and critical father visits his son at his new job as sheriff.

title: Chip's Damage
description: Elodie enlists KO to help figure out what to do about Chip Damage.

title: Say Hello to my Little Friends
description: After telling the kids he will not miss them over the long weekend Chef locks himself into the school and finds out he was very, very wrong.

title: I Am My Monster
description: Everything is not fine.

title: Alan
description: Darwin wants to put Alan on the cover of the school yearbook - but Alan's apparent modesty gets in the way. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: Que No Pare La Musica
description: Ben y Gwen están entusiasmados por ir al concierto de EDM en el Día de la Tierra en Portland, hasta que Lord Decibel, el villano que manipula el sonido, se apodera del concierto cuando intenta usar el sonido como un arma para destruir el planeta.

title: Scooter Madness
description: Pocoyo and Pato find Elly's scooter and decide to take it back to her. Pato enjoys showing off his scooter skills and quickly forgets who it belongs to. Pato's scooter tricks get bigger and bigger until eventually he breaks the scooter into pieces. Pocoyo and Pato try to fix the scooter but it's no good. However will they tell Elly? At first they try to cover up what they've done but eventually they have to confess. Thankfully Elly is not upset with them as she has another scooter and is just pleased her friends told the truth in the end.

title: Meet Tanya Keys
description: When bounty hunter Tanya Keys comes to town for Badgerclops, it's up to Mao Mao and Adorabat to save their friend -- even if he's been on the wrong side of the law.

title: Mystery Girl
description: After Clarence and pals call random numbers as a prank, Clarence ends up connecting with a girl and they strike up a friendship. But will this long distance phone pal last?

title: Butterfly
description: Bing and his friends are playing at Amma's today when a beautiful butterfly comes inside. But what happens when Bing catches the butterfly in his hands while trying to save it?

title: The Prodigal Father
description: Zane, kidnapped by the Mechanic, faces Unagami. Master Wu fights to free Zane, while Pixal questions Milton Dyer for information on how to shut down Prime Empire.

title: Scary Noises
description: Pocoyo and Pato are out for an adventure in the Vamoosh but have to land on a strange planet when a part of the Vamoosh falls off. Whilst searching for the missing part, Pato gets scared because he hears a strange, scary noise. They both realize there is nothing to be scared of and the alien just wants to make friends.

title: Finding Aquaman
description: While searching for a missing Aquaman, the Titans find themselves at the mercy of Black Manta.

title: Soy Mi Monstruo
description: No todo está bien.

title: Charlene Mania
description: When Vic attempts to have the perfect day off, the town's sudden obsession for Charlene gets in his way.

title: The Beepers: Funky Time
description: The Beepers play with tempo and learn that adapting to change can be…sweaty.

title: Boingo/Findley's Bad Day/You Rang
description: Lucas, Findley and Bodhi become obsessed with a new toy called Boingo./ Findley is convinced House is out to get him./ Arlo is missing his mother, so Lucas gives him a bell to ring if he needs Lucas's help - bad idea.

title: El ultimo en Salir De Ciudad Playa
description: Perla, Steven y Amatista van a un concierto de rock.

title: Big Kid Caillou/Caillou's Glasses/Caillou's Dance Party
description: Caillou's older friend Andre is coming over to play./When Mommy gets a new pair of specs, Caillou wants glasses too./Miss Martin is throwing a dance party.

title: El Amo
description: Los Watterson juegan un juego de rol fantástico para resolver sus diferencias.
originalseriesname: The Amazing World of Gumball en Espanol

title: Taco Comet
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang go undercover to taste the most sought after treat in the cosmos: the Taco Comet.

title: Stakes Part 8: The Dark Cloud
description: The final confrontation! Who will survive?

title: We Baby Bears Official Trailer: New Series
description: These baby bears are searching for a brand new home, and they're off to fantastical worlds and new adventures along the way. Watch the official trailer for We Baby Bears, the brand new show from the creators of We Bare Bears, coming to Cartoon Network in 2022.

title: Stop, Drop and Side Scroll
description: Our ninja barely have time to mourn the loss of their fallen ninja friends before being thrust into the madness of Terra Domina where Lloyd will have to face an old adversary from his past.

title: Rainy Boots
description: It's a wet, drippy day and Bing has his rainy boots on to help Flop take the trash out. While splish splashing outside, what will happen when Bing does a BIG SPLASH and finds his rainy boots have holes in them?

title: Alpha Bodies
description: Cartoonito presents Alpha Bodies! It's time to use our bodies to make every letter of the alphabet, from A to Z, but one over-eager letter keeps getting ahead of itself.

title: Blippi Learns Rainbow Colors
description: Have you ever wondered how a rainbow gets its colors? Join Blippi and his sidekick TABBS on their first adventure as they discover the science behind rainbows!

title: The Substitute
description: After Ms. Baker takes an unexpected personal day, she is replaced by a substitute that has a hard time handling the unruly classroom. Soon, the school day devolves into chaos and it is up to Clarence to get Mrs. Baker back to where she belongs, the classroom.

title: Banana Joe
description: When Principal Brown sets Darwin the task of making the school yearbook, Darwin starts by asking class clown Banana Joe for a simple selfie to put on the cover. But with Banana Joe, things are never that simple. Featuring hilarious clips from the first six seasons of 'The Amazing World of Gumball'.

title: An American Benwolf in London
description: Ben and Rook are called to London England to investigate the Forever Knights' latest activities.

title: Reunited
description: Steven brings everyone together for a special reunion.

title: Drawn to Sports with Olivia
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating young athletes from all over the country who are Drawn to Sports! Olivia is a tennis player who is also passionate about art.

title: Special Delivery
description: After being rudely interrupted by Bim Bom during her daily morning song, an angry Unikitty takes the advice of her friends and writes down her feelings into a letter with the intention of keeping the letter to herself, but then accidentally sends it off, complete with postage! The gang then goes on a wild chase through the Unikingdom mail delivery service to keep that rude letter from getting into the hands of Bim Bom, and ultimately hurting her feelings. Turns out, Unikitty's "rude" is everyone else's "nice" and the letter was full of compliments.

title: DC Super Hero Girls: Super Hero High
description: Supergirl arrives at Super Hero High and struggles to learn to control her new powers. Meanwhile, the Junior Detective Club investigates a mysterious rash of security breaches centered around the teleportation Boom Tubes.

title: The Speedway Five-Billion
description: Unagami's soldiers, the Red Visors, finally discover the secret location of Scott's garage and attack the ninja, who manage to escape with the help of Racer Seven, and enter the spectacular Speedway Five Billion.

title: Memories of Bobby
description: When a pillar of the Creek community leaves, our trio mourns their loss by remembering the good times.

title: #MultipliciZee
description: Zee magically duplicates herself so she can shirk work and watch TV. Things get out of hand when her copies start to make copies of themselves!

title: Arma de Eleccion
description: Preocupado de que su espada sea un premio consuelo con pretensiones, Mao Mao decide salir a demostrar el valor de su arma.

title: Bouncing Back
description: Mush-Mush is very proud he invented a new game called Fruity Bounce, where he and his friends bounce as high as possible on the bouncier fruits they can find. Little did he know, the Mushups were fruit-bouncing way before he, Chep and Lilit did. So, Mush-Mush decides that if he can't be the inventor of the game, he'll at least be the best at it. Mushlers vs Mushups, game on!

title: The Escape Room of Doom
description: The gang infiltrate an escape room game center to thwart Score Creeper, but their former foe claims he only works there to pay the bills.

title: Change Your Mind
description: Steven faces his biggest challenge yet.

title: Lucky Stars
description: Raven explains astrology to the Titans and tells their horoscopes, but Cyborg does not believe.

title: #AcceptNoSubstitute
description: Feeling smothered, Babs urges her retired dad, Commissioner Gordon, to get a hobby, but her advice backfires when the Commissioner becomes a substitute teacher at her school!

title: The Mysterious Revenger/Wynton vs. Lia
description: The Mysterious Revenger: It's the quarter finals of the Bakugan Battle League, the top eight brawlers are set to face off! In this round, Dan will face off against the Bakugan rocker - Revenger! These two brawlers give it their all in this icy cold clash!/Wynton Vs. Lia: The quarter finals continue, and it's the first Awesome Brawler vs. Awesome Brawler matches of the Bakugan Battle League tournament. In this round, it's Wynton vs. Lia and Shun vs. Lightning.

title: The Man
description: It's Granny Jojo's Birthday and she's brought an unexpected guest to dinner. Granny Jojo has brought a boyfriend to her birthday meal and Dad isn't happy about it. He bans Granny JoJo from ever seeing Louis again. When the kids get caught sneaking Granny Jojo out of the house, Dad challenges Louis to a man-off to prove once and for all who is the man of the house?!!

title: Tough Luck
description: Gwen's Lucky Girl powers return when she buys a magical stone at a magic convention in Las Vegas. However, Hex is after the same stone, and after his niece breaks him out of prison, the two set off to retrieve the stone.

title: Caillou Makes a Meal/Caillou's New Groove/Caillou Goes Bowling
description: Caillou makes pizza for dinner with his family./Mommy and Daddy are gone overnight and Grandpa and Grandma are babysitting./Caillou is hesitant to try bowling.

title: Conozcan a Tanya Keys
description: Cuando Tanya Keys, la cazadora de recompensas, llega a la ciudad para atrapar a Colosal, Mao Mao y Adorabat son los encargados de salvar a su amigo... aunque se haya metido en asuntos ilegales.

title: Hello Around the World
description: Cartoonito presents Hello Around the World! All across the globe, friends greet each other in lots of different languages. Watch along and discover some of the many ways to say "Hello," around the world and beyond!

title: El Padre Prodigo
description: Zane, secuestrado por el Mecánico mientras Pixal interroga a Milton Dyer para obtener información sobre cómo cerrar el Primer Imperio.

title: Rebel Rebel
description: The Professor makes new friends, but they may be the wrong crowd.

title: Nos Capturaron
description: Box-man captura a K.O., Enid y Rad, pero parece un poco distraído.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Beepers: Spotlight
description: When a spotlight gives everyone a chance to solo, a shy Beeper discovers the courage to shine.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Lorenzo
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Lorenzo tells us about his passion for reggaetón music and soccer.

title: The New Nemesis
description: When Hawkodile discovers his old enemy Eagleator has a new nemesis in his life, the gang do all they can to get Hawk back on his foe's radar.

title: Carrera Cinco Billones por Hora
description: Los soldados de Unagami, los Visores Rojos, finalmente descubren la ubicación secreta del garaje de Scott y atacan a los Ninjas.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Julian
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Rushing the Raspberry/Wait to Skate/Caillou's Hiccups
description: Caillou is helping Mommy take care of a raspberry bush./Daddy is building an ice rink in the backyard./A spaghetti dinner (and a lot of giggling) result in Caillou getting the hiccups.

title: Morel in the Dark
description: When Mush-Mush discovers that Morel is afraid of the dark, he suggests that Chep, Lilit and he take the Mushlets to their first overnight forest camp. Morel is relieved. But when Mush-Mush and his friends later come back, panicked, and reveal that the Mushlets have disappeared, Morel has no choice but to face his fear and join our friends on their rescue mission in the dark!

title: Bobo Chan
description: Colosal adopta a un monstruo abandonado, pero es mejor dejar algunas cosas en estado salvaje.

title: Don't Laze Me, Bro
description: Ben and his arch-enemy Billy Billions clash in a duel for supremacy at the world's largest Laser Tag Park, LASER TOWN. But, when Billy inadvertently ignites a robot rebellion, and the lasers are set from tag to disintegrate, their childish game escalates into a full blown war! The two foes find that they must set aside their petty differences and team up in order to make it out alive, let alone save the day!

title: Uncle Grandpa's Odd-yssey
description: Uncle Grandpa and the gang must retrieve Tiger from the pound before she's adopted out.

title: Legend of Torbaclaun
description: When the Sweetypies think the mythical Torbaclaun has come to Pure Heart Valley, Mao Mao tries to prove to them that it isn't real.

title: El Templo de la Locura
description: Jay debe enfrentarse solo a Unagami en el juego final, pero Unagami tiene una batalla más grande al enfrentarse a la verdad sobre su propia identidad.

title: Fortachones

title: Penny Ruda
description: Ben visita el Gran Desfile Anual Big Bacon, pero Penny Heaven, su "amiga" de la infancia, se reúne con la familia para estropear la diversión de Ben con su obsesión por la seguridad. Mientras Ben esquiva las medidas de seguridad extremas de Penny, devela un plan de los HERMANOS BUGG, ique intentan robar helio de los globos del desfile para usarlos en robos de bancos! La insistencia de Penny convierte el ataque en un secuestro accidental, de modo que Ben no solo debe impedir el robo sino también salvar a su "supervisora de seguridad" menos querida.

title: Kung Fu Master/A Battle of Popularity

His opponent is a deeply focused, and serious brawler, who uses Kung Fu techniques in battle. It's going to take all Dan and Drago's focus and strength to get through this opponent!/A Battle of Popularity: Shun and Wynton's first match-ups in the Bakugan battle league take place at the same time. Even though they're not battling each other, Wynton can't help getting a little competitive with Shun, bragging that he can get the crowd cheering louder than Shun. The brawls quickly turn into a popularity contest, instead of a Bakugan battle!

title: La noche de fiesta de los villanos
description: Lord Box-man entra a la fuerza en una fiesta exclusiva para villanos.
originalseriesname: OK K.O.! Let's Be Heroes en Espanol

title: The Bakugan Battle League Begins/Riot vs. Ajit

The Awesome Brawlers all make it through into the tournament without a hitch, that is all but Dan. Dan faces an old rival in Trey, who's back with a few tricks up his sleeve./Riot vs. Ajit: The Bakugan battle league is finally here and 16 brawlers have qualified to enter including all the Awesome Brawlers. The first round will feature a brawl between China Riot and the golden Bakugan brawler, Agit!

title: Pouting Match
description: Lola tries pouting to get what she wants, and soon all the babies are doing it.

title: Drawn To Juneteenth: Ms. Opal
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Juneteenth! Juneteenth commemorates the end of slavery with celebrations that take place every year on June 19th! This holiday recognizes the day that all slaves were free in the U.S.! We are recognizing those who are dedicated to making this special holiday known as they are Drawn to...Juneteenth!

title: Squirrels Squirrels Squirrels

title: Potato

description: Melissa wants cake, but she wants the other babies to bake it for her.

title: Drawn To Rhythm: Jayleen
description: Cartoon Network is celebrating Hispanic Heritage Month with another installment of "Drawn To" that showcases kids who honor their Hispanic and Latino heritage as they are drawn to rhythm. In this piece, Jayleen shows us some of the eight different dance styles she can do, including bachata and cumbia.

title: Dragonhead

While dodging Penny's overzealous safety precautions, Ben uncovers a plot by the Bug Brothers to steal helium from the parade balloons to rob banks with! Penny's badgering turns the heist into an accidental kidnapping so Ben must not only stop the robbery but save his least favorite safety monitor in the process.

title: La Leyenda del Torbaclaun

title: Entremedias

title: Detective Pocoyo

While Pocoyo goes back to the scene of the crime, Elly finds that she had her doll all along: it wasn't lost at all, she'd simply mislaid it. Elly is too embarrassed to own up and tells Pocoyo she doesn't need her doll anymore. But Detective Pocoyo uncovers the truth and the mystery is solved.

title: High Score

description: When a race of alien mushrooms takes over a summer camp, Ben discovers a whole new alien to battle the menace.

title: No Me Ataques, Amigo

Pero cuando, sin darse cuenta, Billy desata una rebelión robótica, y los lásers pasan de tocar a desintegrar, isu juego infantil se convierte en una guerra sin cuartel! Los enemigos descubren que deben dejar de lado sus diferencias y unirse para poder salir con vida...iy salvar al resto del planeta!

title: Drawn to Making it Happen with Sidney Keys
description: Cartoon Network celebrates Black History Month with Sidney Keys III, a 15-year-old rising entrepreneur and the founder and CEO of "Books n Bros," an African American literature book club for male youth ages 7-13 years old. Focused on promoting literacy among young Black boys and introducing them to positive representation in literature, Keys' advocacy is paving the way for change by creating a place for boys to be mentored by their "Big Bros" and connect over a shared love for reading.

The shock of this accusation sets Magnus off to takes justice in his own hands and go after the thief himself./Magnus foils the latest burglary attempt by the phantom thief, and in doing so, discovers the brawler partners with a golden Bakugan.  Magnus is now more interested in a brawl, than stopping any crime.

When the directions turn out to be wrong and lead them into danger, Cheer must trust her instincts to find a way out of the mess.

title: The Master
description: Dad decides to resolve the Watterson family's differences through the power and magic of his favorite roleplaying game. As they embark on the adventure of a lifetime and battle mythical creatures, will they finally manage to put their differences aside and work together?
